{"title":"Explosive Bolt","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Explosive_Bolt","type":"markdown","data":"***Obsolete**: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.*\n\n| Explosive Bolt                              |                                                         |\n| :------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Level                                       | 6                                                       |\n| School1                                     | [Conjuration](/Conjurations \"Conjurations\")             |\n| School2                                     | [Fire](/Fire_Magic \"Fire Magic\")                        |\n| School3                                     |                                                         |\n| Source(s)                                   | - [Rod of ignition](/Rod_of_ignition \"Rod of ignition\") |\n| [Casting noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\") | 6                                                       |\n| [Spell noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")   | 15                                                      |\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                        |\n| - | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | This spell hurls a bolt containing fiery energy; on piercing a target, it lets loose an explosion that harms nearby creatures as well. |\n\n**Explosive Bolt** is a level 6 spell only available through a [rod of ignition](/Rod_of_ignition \"Rod of ignition\"). Each target it hits will cause a 3×3 explosion on the target, as through struck by [Fireball](/Fireball \"Fireball\").\n\nWhile it doesn't have perfect accuracy, it can tear through a cramped group of opponents. Also note that the exp