e class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> Explosive Bolt\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Level\n</th>\n<td> 6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>1</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Conjurations\" title=\"Conjurations\">Conjuration</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>2</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Fire_Magic\" title=\"Fire Magic\">Fire</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>3</sup>\n</th>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Source(s)\n</th>\n<td><div>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Rod_of_ignition\" title=\"Rod of ignition\">Rod of ignition</a> </li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Casting noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Spell noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 15\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> This spell hurls a bolt containing fiery energy; on piercing a target, it lets loose an explosion that harms nearby creatures as well.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Explosive Bolt</b> is a level 6 spell only available through a <a href=\"/Rod_of_ignition\" title=\"Rod of ignition\">rod of ignition</a>. Each target it hits will cause a 3×3 explosion on the target, as through struck by <a href=\"/Fireball\" title=\"Fireball\">Fireball</a>.\n</p><p>While it doesn't have perfect accuracy, it can tear through a cramped group of opponents. Also note that the explosions can hurt you, so try to avoid using it against melee opponents.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Explosive Bolt was removed in <a href=\"/0.20\" title=\"0.20\">0.20</a>, alon